name: Mexican Lasagna 1
ingredients: 2/3 cups diced tomato and green chilies
1 can cream of chicken and cream of mushroom soup
instructions: Cook the breast, beans, garlic powder, tomato, and cumin.
Cook soups and enchilada sauce for 10 minutes.
Spread with half the chicken, a third of the sauce, half the cheese, top with 3 tortillas layers end with tortillas.
Top with extra cheese and  cook for a few more minutes.
